From Cosmopolitan Shortly after President Donald Trump signed an executive order calling for an immediate immigration and refugee ban targeting Muslim-majority countries, an old tweet from Trump Hotels' Twitter account asking followers for their "favorite travel memory" went viral - for exactly the reason you might expect.
Tell us your favorite travel memory - was it a picture, a souvenir, a sunset? We'd love to hear it!
- Trump Hotels (@TrumpHotels) October 11, 2011 Over the weekend, thousands responded to the 2011 tweet with scathing, heartbreaking, and powerful stories which made it perfectly clear just how many people are against Trump's ban and what it represents. You can read a few of those responses below.
